        "en": "1. Market Analysis<br>2. E-commerce website setup and management<br>3. Google Analytics data analysis<br>4. Google Basic Digital Marketing Qualification<br>5. Google Ads Search Advertising Certification<br>6. Implementation of e-commerce rack station"
